---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Groups - PKKBN 2026">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-12 pt-12 pb-24">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary">Pembagian Gugus</h1>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">
        Informasi lengkap tentang pembagian gugus dalam PKKBN
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Overview Card -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container text-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">groups</span>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">100 Gugus</h2>
          <p class="text-primary-fixed opacity-90">Mahasiswa baru dibagi ke dalam 100 gugus</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Group Composition -->
    <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined bg-secondary/10 text-secondary p-2 rounded-xl">group</span>
        Komposisi Gugus
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mt-1">check_circle</span>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">
            Setiap gugus terdiri dari mahasiswa baru yang berasal dari <strong>beberapa program studi</strong> yang berbeda.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mt-1">check_circle</span>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">
            Setiap gugus didampingi oleh <strong>Kakak Asuh</strong>.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Kakak Asuh Role -->
    <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest px-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined bg-tertiary-fixed-dim/30 text-on-tertiary-container p-2 rounded-xl">person_pin</span>
        Peran Kakak Asuh
      </h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-4">
        Segala hal yang berkaitan dengan PKKBN harus diinformasikan kepada Kakak Asuh, termasuk:
      </p>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container-low p-4 rounded-xl">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-fixed-dim">event_busy</span>
          <span>Ketidakhadiran (berhalangan hadir)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container-low p-4 rounded-xl">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-fixed-dim">sick</span>
          <span>Sakit</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container-low p-4 rounded-xl">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-fixed-dim">alarm</span>
          <span>Terlambat</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container-low p-4 rounded-xl">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-fixed-dim">more_horiz</span>
          <span>Dan lain-lain</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- NIM-based Division -->
    <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest px-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined bg-primary/10 text-primary p-2 rounded-xl">tag</span>
        Dasar Pembagian Gugus
      </h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
        Pembagian gugus didasarkan pada <strong>3 (tiga) digit terakhir NIM</strong> mahasiswa.
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
              <th class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-on-surface-variant">Digit Akhir NIM</th>
              <th class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-on-surface-variant">Gugus</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-sm">
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container-low">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono">001, 101, 201, 301, 401, ...</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-primary">Gugus 1</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container-low">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono">002, 102, 202, 302, 402, ...</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-primary">Gugus 2</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container-low">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono">003, 103, 203, 303, 403, ...</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-primary">Gugus 3</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/10">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-on-surface-variant italic">...</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 text-on-surface-variant italic">...</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-surface-container-low">
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-mono">100, 200, 300, 400, ...</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-primary">Gugus 100</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Example -->
    <div class="bg-secondary-container/20 border border-secondary/30 p-6 rounded-2xl">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">lightbulb</span>
        Contoh
      </h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant">
        Jika NIM mahasiswa adalah <strong class="font-mono bg-surface-container-low px-2 py-1 rounded">123045</strong>, maka mahasiswa tersebut masuk ke dalam <strong class="text-secondary">Gugus 45</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Note -->
    <div class="text-center italic text-on-surface-variant text-sm border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-6">
      <p>Dokumen ini menjelaskan sistem pembagian gugus dalam PKKBN UPN "Veteran" Yogyakarta.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
